{\\text{R}}$), and left- and\nright-handed tensor ($g_{\\text{L}},g_{\\text{R}}$) tWb couplings is set while\nfixing all others to their standard model values. The allowed regions are\n[$-$0.11, 0.16] for $V_{\\text{R}}$, [$-$0.08, 0.05] for $g_{\\text{L}}$, and\n[$-$0.04, 0.02] for $g_{\\text{R}}$, at 95% confidence level. Limits on the\ncorresponding Wilson coefficients are also derived.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 23:45:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Sep 2020 14:03:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-25"}
