chical model can\nachieve better results than the flat model for multi-category diagnosis of GI\ndisorders using histopathological images.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 06:05:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 01:28:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-10"}
