, faster and more accurate. Finally, we evaluate the\nactual performance on an Android smartphone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 10:30:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 14:21:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 04:40:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-06"}
